{"tid":202232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合國維和部隊涉2千件性侵案,性侵300名兒童難民","createTime":"2017-04-15T10:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T12:54:13.000Z","uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ed5351d07c372ef13de1d0c5580504801f909238","tid":202232,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:47:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=242765\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D242765&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=ebfec129\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D242765&h=5304969d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=242765</a><br />\n<br />\n根據《美聯社》最新公布的一項資料顯示，致力為遭受衝突的國家創造和平、幫助受害平民百姓的維和部隊，過去12年來涉及的性侵案竟超過2000件，其中多達300件涉及兒童。據報導指出，一名受害少女表示，當時年僅12歲的她被迫與維和部隊士兵發生性行為，其中還包括司令官，稱自己3年期間共遭50名士兵性侵。<br />\n<br />\n近年維和部隊爭議不斷，屢傳不人道的行為，去年南蘇丹瀕臨內戰，傳出派駐在當地的維和部隊竟對遭軍隊攻擊的平民見死不救，坐視老百姓被殺，甚至任由數百名婦女慘遭性侵，如今又傳出性侵醜聞，有違維和部隊宗旨的行為引發爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解無左膠屌下佢地??"},{"pid":"b7bdad6c91c4928f254bb0343d910b8b845e77c0","tid":202232,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:55:18.000Z","msg":"諾貝爾和平獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7377c1a157ba0a5b23044da773eaec3f9b47da97","tid":202232,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:59:47.000Z","msg":"維和部隊偷運武器都試過 有乜做唔出<br />\n印尼維和部隊士兵‧圖私運武器蘇丹被捕<br />\n<a href=\"http://indonesia.sinchew.com.my/node/64707?tid=5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Findonesia.sinchew.com.my%2Fnode%2F64707%3Ftid%3D5&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=0efeb237\" target=\"_blank\">http://indonesia.sinchew.com.my/node/64707?tid=5</a><br />\n<br />\n聯合國將&ldquo;處分&rdquo;走私武器維和部隊<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.crntt.com/doc/1003/7/4/2/100374267.html?coluid=70&amp;kindid=1850&amp;docid=100374267&amp;mdate=0911123624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.crntt.com%2Fdoc%2F1003%2F7%2F4%2F2%2F100374267.html%3Fcoluid%3D70%26kindid%3D1850%26docid%3D100374267%26mdate%3D0911123624&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c8612c9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.crntt.com/doc/1003/7/4/2/100374267.html?coluid=70&amp;kindid=1850&amp;docid=100374267&amp;mdate=0911123624</a>"},{"pid":"164e9adcf62681af81d2773aa8d7bb4e62aba9b6","tid":202232,"uid":3668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-oWwRpjkrJcs/T_DHcRWgonI/AAAAAAAAEj0/AfiHBx5tPjk/s1600/un+uninvolved+in+peace.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-oWwRpjkrJcs%2FT_DHcRWgonI%2FAAAAAAAAEj0%2FAfiHBx5tPjk%2Fs1600%2Fun%2Buninvolved%2Bin%2Bpeace.jpg&h=1397fe2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"058c4c8109440e0f13d98cab2c357a43e2f8733c","tid":202232,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:03:32.000Z","msg":"重有大把國家組織用人道物資名義運武器 之前俄羅斯送食物比east ukraine比人見到有一車車T72同anti-air係後面過邊界"},{"pid":"6fd225e968a7aebfdc0138843745a4b2d7fc4179","tid":202232,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:43:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重有大把國家組織用人道物資名義運武器 之前俄羅斯送食物比east ukraine比人見到有一車車T72同anti-air係後面過邊界</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然係仆街<br />\n但呢D唔關「維和部隊」既事<br />\n<br />\n「維和部隊」 係由聯合國指揮, 頭盔係藍色, 方便容易認"},{"pid":"ba740229b0aab88204275681b92732aaab22fb4f","tid":202232,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/f45DV6D.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ff45DV6D.gif&h=e7c42a7d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}